    • Method Detail

      • onDecryptSecureBeacons

        void onDecryptSecureBeacons(java.util.List<DiscoveryData> decryptedDiscoveryDataList,
                            int decryptedCount)
        Will be called if BlukiiClient.decryptSecureBeacons(List, OnDecryptSecureBeaconsListener) is successfully requested. Parameter decryptedDiscoveryDataList contains all list items contained as parameter in BlukiiClient.decryptSecureBeacons(List, OnDecryptSecureBeaconsListener). If the authenticated blukii Manager user is owner of list items that are marked with DiscoveryData.getSecureBeaconState() as SecureBeaconState.ENCRYPTED, these are decrypted.
        Parameters:
        decryptedDiscoveryDataList - result list of discoveryData objects.
        decryptedCount - count of items that are decrypted.

      • onError

        void onError(BlukiiCloudError error)
        Will be called if BlukiiClient.decryptSecureBeacons(List, OnDecryptSecureBeaconsListener) requested has done with errors.
        Parameters:
        error - BlukiiCloudError result code.
